     C                     DO
      *
     C                     SETOF                     313249
JW1  C                     SETOF                     333435
     C                     TIME           WSDT
      *
     C* DATE FROM
     C           F1SCFH    IFEQ *ZERO
     C           F1SCFH    ORGT WSSDAT
     C                     SETON                     3149
